payload: Please be advised that Ken Raisler from Sullivan and Cromwell will be conducting Sales Practices/Anti-Manipulation Training sessions this week for the commercial staff. The program covers the legal implications of various activities of our commercial team -- particularly as they interact with customers in marketing. The program also covers laws prohibiting market manipulation that might affect our trading and marketing activities. The two hour training sessions will be held at the Doubletree, in the Dezavala Room on the second floor at the listed times. Please feel free to attend and observe (since legal staff are more likely to know the answers, you are asked not to participate in the break-out small group sessions). Session 1 Thursday, Sept. 14 2:00 p.m. Session 2 Thursday, Sept. 14 4:00 p.m. Session 3 Friday, Sept. 15 9:00 a.m. Session 4 Friday, Sept. 15 2:00 p.m. Please feel free to contact me at X57373 or Mark Taylor at X37459 if you have any questions. Best regards, Taffy Milligan
